column2: Data cleansing is performed through several steps. First, the data is loaded and checked for missing and blank values in the complaints column. Blank values are replaced with NaN and then dropped from the dataframe. The complaint_what_happened is converted to string for performing text operations. Additionally, the texts are then preprocessed using several techniques including making the text lowercase, removing text in square brackets, removing punctuation, and removing words containing numbers. After this, the texts are lemmatized and POS tags are used to get relevant words from the text.
